{"meta":{"domain":"subjects","kid":"5093","authors":[{"fullname":"Nicolas Tournadre","id":"6"}],"title":"","dates":{"created_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:21 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:21 UTC"}},"nodes":[{"index":0,"parent_index":-1,"body":"<p class=\"Paragraph\">This verb, which means \u201cto want,\u201d requires the main verb to be in the present-future.<\/p><p class=\"Paragraph\">It appears only as a modal verb (and not as a main verb), and may be combined with the following auxiliaries. It functions in a similar way to the verb <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f51\u0f42\u0f7c\u0f66\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cneed.\u201d<\/p><ul> <li>in the present: <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f60\u0f51\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f61\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b<\/span> (egophoric), <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f60\u0f51\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f60\u0f51\u0f74\u0f42\u0f0b<\/span>, or <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f60\u0f51\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f61\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0b<\/span><\/li> <li>in the past: <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f60\u0f51\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f56\u0fb1\u0f74\u0f44\u0f0b<\/span> (egophoric), <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f60\u0f51\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f56\u0fb1\u0f74\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f66\u0f7c\u0f44\u0f0b<\/span>, or <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f60\u0f51\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f56\u0fb1\u0f74\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f56\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0b<\/span><\/li> <li>in the future: <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f60\u0f51\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f40\u0fb1\u0f72\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0b<\/span><\/li> <\/ul><p class=\"Paragraph\">The perfective past auxiliaries <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f66\u0f7c\u0f44\u0f0b<\/span>, <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f54\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0b<\/span>, and <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0f5e\u0f42\u0f0b<\/span> may not directly follow the verb <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f60\u0f51\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b<\/span>. The following constructions are thus wrong: *<span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f60\u0f51\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f66\u0f7c\u0f44\u0f0b<\/span> *<span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f60\u0f51\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f54\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0b<\/span> *<span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f60\u0f51\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f56\u0f5e\u0f42\u0f0b<\/span>. These example sentences are correct:<\/p><ul> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f42\u0f44\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f4f\u0f72\u0f0b\u0f66\u0f7a\u0f62\u0f0b\u0f60\u0f42\u0fb2\u0f7c\u0f0b\u0f60\u0f51\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f61\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0d<\/span> \u201cI want to go to Kailash.\u201d<\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f41\u0fb1\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f5a\u0f7c\u0f0b\u0f56\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f63\u0f0b\u0f55\u0f7a\u0f56\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f60\u0f51\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f61\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f54\u0f66\u0f0d<\/span> \u201cWould you like to go to Tibet?\u201d<\/li> <\/ul>","title":""}]}